        <h2> 1. Background</h2>
        <p>
          CSP globally (large-scale) -> CSP small scale -> Industry partner issues (interview w/ Mr Tan and add images) (Vietnam and Indonesia). Talk about the uses of CSP, existing solutions, and problems. We are using unit measurement (1x1m scale rig), for this, mention why scalability is good (this section or motivations section?).
        </p>
